; Simple 100 x 100 mm square
; With scale=0.001 in gcode.cfg this draws a 10 cm square.
;
;  (0,100) _________ (100,100)
;         |         |
;         |         |
;  (0,0)  |_________| (100,0)
;
; Z > 0  → travel (arm lifted)
; Z < 0  → draw  (force/admittance mode)

G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; travel to bottom-left, lifted
G01 X0 Y0 Z-1       ; touch down at (0,0)
G01 X100 Y0         ; bottom edge →
G01 X100 Y100       ; right edge  ↑
G01 X0 Y100         ; top edge    ←
G01 X0 Y0           ; left edge   ↓  back to start
G00 X0 Y0 Z10       ; lift off
